I got informants.

146
00:08:18.562 --> 00:08:20.258
but I don't have a
fucking strike team.

147
00:08:20.259 --> 00:08:22.565
Fine. I'll call Federal
Police in Mexico

148
00:08:22.566 --> 00:08:23.740
