149
00:08:23.741 --> 00:08:25.046
See how that works out.

150
00:08:25.047 --> 00:08:26.830
All right. all right.

151
00:08:26.831 --> 00:08:28.789
Let me. uh. let me make a
call. see what I can do.

152
00:08:28.790 --> 00:08:30.618
